cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.CV. 

The paper deals with similarity computations across large sets of documents, which is a common problem in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of GPUs for acceleration suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and data science (cs.DS) applications. Finally, the mention of real-life datasets and the potential for image analysis (cs.CV) also make this a possible category.
